    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Investigator Talents - Studied Combat/Strike</strong><br/><br/><p>When the investigator deals damage with studied strike, the opponent must succeed at a Fortitude save (DC = 10 + 1/2 the investigator's class level + his Intelligence modif ier) or be slowed by the crippling blow. A slowed opponent's movement speeds are each reduced by 5 feet (to a minimum of 5 feet) until the creature is healed through the application of any spell that cures hit point damage or with a successful DC 15 Heal check. Multiple slowing strikes stack, to a minimum of 5 feet. An investigator must be at least 7th level to select this talent.</p>",
